{
  "texts": [
    "The research team formed a multidisciplinary team consisting of a thyroid cancer pharmacist, a nursing specialist, a thyroid cancer physician, and a public health specialist to discuss and develop the intervention program.",
    "The control group received routine medical and nursing care, and the intervention group received the MTM-based mHealth intervention in addition to routine medical care.",
    "The intervention group receives MTM-mHealth, and the realization of health education will rely on the smart terminal WeChat platform.",
    "Combined with the chat communication function of WeChat, timely communication between physicians and patients will be realized, and patients' concerns will be answered by physicians or professional nurses in a timely manner.",
    "At the same time, through the WeChat platform, physicians or professional nurses can realize timely interventions for patients, including daily reminders of medication taking, popularization of thyroid cancer-related science, and interpretation of cutting-edge research on thyroid cancer."
  ]
}